summary: The script provides a workflow for transforming Stable Diffusion ControlNet models, including standard and XL UNet variants, from PyTorch implementations into ONNX format. It defines model wrappers, performs graph optimizations to remove redundancies and infer shapes, and handles the export process with version checks and file management.
